  It is easier to get forgiveness than permission.  Revenge is a dish best served cold If you get it overnight, you can lose it just as quick  Like a roaring lion or a charging bear is a wicked man ruling over a helpless people Different strokes for different folk The best throw of the dice is to throw them away  You catch more flies with honey than with vinegar People living in glass houses should not pelt stones. When two buffalo fight, it is the grass that gets hurt! Home is where you hang your @. 
